== BasecampCalendarCreateV1
   This handler allows you to create a calendar in Basecamp.

=== Parameters
    [Calendar Name]
          The name of the calendar you wish to add. (must be unique)
			
=== Results
    No results are returned for this handler.
	
    An exception is raised if there is an existing calendar with the requested name.

==== Sample Configuration
     Calendar Name: New Calendar

=== Detailed Description
    This handler creates a new calendar for Basecamp. If there is an existing
    calendar with the requested name an exception will be raised.
	
===  Getting Your User Id Number
	1. In a browser, login to your account.
		here : https://launchpad.37signals.com/basecamp/signin
	2. In the url, your user id comes right after the host name.
		ex. https://basecamp.com/#######/etc
			https://hostname.com/user_id/...
